
A simple project to explore HTML5's Canvas, which changes the question
for making graphical programs which can be accessed by virtually any
platform and device.

This was inspired by Mark Pilgrim's
<a href="http://diveintohtml5.info/index.html">"Dive into HTML5"</a>
and <a href="http://hakim.se/experiments/">Hakim El Hattab</a>.</p>
